title: Winning Blog Tactics Free Online Marketing Strategy Guide
description:
The 2014 edition of the [b]Free Online Marketing Strategy Guide[/b] by Winning Blog Tactics.

First created as a teaching tool for my team, this free online marketing strategy guide will walk you, step by step through the process of [u]creating your own online marketing platform[/u] from scratch, and teach you [u]how to effectively market anything in just 1 to 2 hours per day[/u].

Mostly free strategies, there are 8 chapters in the book which covers in depth topics from search engines and local marketing, to social bookmarking, social media, classifieds, and more.

I even teach my own personal strategy for converting offline marketing faster with mobile technology I created.

This is just the first chapter, and the link to download the full book (also free) is in the torrent.

Download it right now and not only get the book for free, but learn how you can get free access to the tools and resources I create for free by being a BETA tester.

I appreciate you guys and I'll see you on the inside!

~Athalos
